{"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","symbolKind":"case","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":[" If a text's language supports horizontal writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out horizontally."]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"abstract":[{"text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingMode","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal","title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}]}}}